  "text": "Senegalese sole has been the subject of thorough research in the last two decades, because of its high market demand, high market value and the adaptability of existent facilities to accommodate its rearing [CITATION_1] . These facts present sole as an interesting new species for diversifying Mediterranean marine aquaculture.",
